snippet.title: Static Cling - Web Version Available Now!
snippet.description:
Newgrounds: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/805099
itch.io: https://team-bugulon.itch.io/static-cling

Play as a rogue spark restrained to electronic devices, running, climbing and stretching through 3 worlds of unique puzzles. Can you free yourself of your electric tethers and escape?

Static Cling OST: https://mistajub.bandcamp.com/album/static-cling

Video edited by Oroshibu :)
